item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Madonna Lossless / 24-Bit Singles & EPs - Quobuz or other reputable quality, NO Tidal / MQA
item.description:
I am requesting the Madonna Singles and EPs re-released by Warner Bros in their highest quality available (24-Bit preferably from Quobuz or another retailer EXCEPT MQA/Tidal). None of the Finally Enough Love promo single releases (which are already in the full album). And no "Material Gwrrol", "Hung Up on Tokischa", or Sam Smith.
